title: RPC_HTTP_TRANSPORT_CREDENTIALS_V2_W (rpcdce.h)
description: The RPC_HTTP_TRANSPORT_CREDENTIALS_V2 structure defines additional credentials to authenticate to an RPC proxy server or HTTP proxy server when using RPC/HTTP.RPC_HTTP_TRANSPORT_CREDENTIALS_V2 extends RPC_HTTP_TRANSPORT_CREDENTIALS by allowing authentication against an HTTP proxy server. (Unicode)
